songs.title: Interlude #1
songs.lyrics:
[Skit: Lil' D]
I had a guy ask me
"Man, I see you on them pictures with Philthy, man
What made you embrace dude?"
And the reason I embraced dude, man, is 'cause I reached out to him when I was in the penitentiary, man
And made a contact with him
We chopped it up, and the dude listened to me, no matter what y’all think of his ego
He take the time to listen to me, man
When I tried to share some game with him, man
Because at the end of the day
I want him to win and I want all my other young folks out here to win, man
But I don't want them to end up where I was at, buried up in them penitentiaries, man
So I tried to share as much wisdom with him as I can
